{"id":572930,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【网络民议】于谦的父亲王老爷子：我心善，见不/","date":"2017-11-26T11:23:49Z","modified":"2017-11-26T11:23:49Z","title":"【网络民议】于谦的父亲王老爷子：我心善，见不了穷人","content":"<p>网易财经：【方圆二十里内不能有穷人<span class=\"url-icon\"><img src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-dcf7d5d0d6.png\" alt=\"[摊手]\" /></span>】郭德纲的相声《怯富贵》里有个段子:于谦的父亲王老爷子家境富裕，立志做天下第一善人，放出话来“别的地方我管不了，但在我住宅方圆二十里之内不能有穷人”。然后，他派人把附近的穷人都赶走了，因为“我心善，见不了穷人”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-572931\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.20.54-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"597\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.20.54-AM.png 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.20.54-AM-300x261.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-572932\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.30-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"599\" height=\"541\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.30-AM.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.30-AM-300x271.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-572933\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.38-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"596\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.38-AM.png 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-26-at-6.21.38-AM-300x235.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 596px) 100vw, 596px\" /></p>\n<div class=\"m-box comment-con-top\">\n<div class=\"m-box-col\">\n<p class=\"comment-user-name\"><span>小分队队长：</span>“我最牵挂的还是困难群众”</p>\n<div class=\"m-box commen